A young Asian boy around 5 years old sitting cross-legged on a wooden floor in a cozy tropical resort setting, looking up with an earnest pleading expression at an open laptop displaying a colorful penguin mascot on screen. The room has bamboo walls and warm afternoon light filtering through woven blinds. In the background, slightly out of focus, stacked refurbished computers ready for donation. The scene has a warm, nostalgic quality with soft golden tones. Studio Ghibli style with gentle watercolor textures, expressive character design with large emotive eyes, and that signature dreamy atmospheric quality with visible dust motes dancing in the sunbeams.
